Hi LJ.
Who comes on here anymore?

Holyshitt, Alie`s... updating??

Yeahh.

I haven`t been on here in ten million years, sorry.
Not like anyone actually reads this shit anyways. xD

School`s shitty, but when`s it not?
My classes suck.
Besides for third period.
Which is Psychology.
It`s really fun, and Mr. Walker is pretty cool.

Mm, yeah.
Erica`s coming over tonight.
So, you know..
haha

What an amazing update.
<3

Wow, I`m actually updating.

=O

 

So summer`s been alright.
Nothing like.. out of the ordinary has happened.

We`re going to Busch Gardens this weekend.
woo. haha

 

<3

YOUR CAUGHT!!! If you REALLY LIKE SOMEONE right now AND MISS THEM and can't get them out of your head then re-post this within 1 mintute and whoever you are missing will surprise you tomorrow.

IF YOU BREAK THIS YOU WILL HAVE THE WORST DAY OF YOUR LIFE TOMORROW!!! 



Ehh. Worth a try. I need some good luck lately. xD

So, I had my last game yesterday. We won, 7-1, which makes it an undefeated season.
A good one too.
&Then coach took us out for dinner, and haha it was so fun.
I`m actually gonna miss those girls. <3

Then I went to Erica`s..
like I do practically every Saturday nite.
God, that girl cracks me up. <3
We watched National Treasure, and she fell asleep, and then she yelled at me for saying she was asleep? xD
Good times.

Yeahhh. I gotta go work on Buice`s project.
I`m gonna miss that class..



<3

So, I`ve heard some pretty crazy things about myself today.
Let`s see, I`m a snobby bitch, apparently a whore, people all around the school want to beat me up, and I`ve recently had a girlfriend.

Geez, I should really start paying attention to these things.

 

 

-_-

Get a fucking life, people.
Seriously, rumors are so childish.
&whoever started these...
Honestly you have to be the most pathetic person I`ve ever come across in my entire life.
&I hope woever`s talking all this shit is reading this, because I`d like them to know that they gave me a good fucking laugh.

hahaha.

Woo, I`m updating. xD Only because I`ve gotten demands from Mark, and JT to do so.. =D

So things have been better than they have in a long time lately.
-Nobody to tie me down
-No gay ass friends to deal with
-No bad grades

I like it..

Progress reports came out. I`m on top of that shit, man.
Geometry- 92%
Marine Bio- 97%
World History- 105%
Dance- We haven`t gotten it yet, but I know I have an A.

I`m all out with the old, in with the new, and I`m really focusing on the things I care about, and not on things that don`t matter anymore.

Props for me.

Leave me comments. Bitch.
<333*

I`ve been listening to all the music that I listened to in 8th grade lately.. Tori Amos, The All-American Rejects, Ani DiFranco.. I`m not complaining though. <3

Hmm let`s see.

Sunday nite I slept over Erica`s. She`s my best friend. My life wold be fucking hell without that girl. [<3] Kym, came over&we smoked ciggs&just talked. It was nice, but I was all quiet `cause I don`t really know Kym too well.

lmao Erica`s dad cracks me up every time I go over there. Last time I went over, I woke up&heard him saying: ``The three things I love to do in life is to eat, to drink&to eat&drink`` xD I almost pissed myself. Then this time, were going outside to walk Kym to the end of the driveway&He screams 'Look, look, it`s ROXY!' -points to TV- -walks into the baby`s hi-chair&breaks it- haha. I love going over there.

Today I read a book called "How I live now." It was... interesting. hah

I have soccer practice tonite. I don`t want to go. I never want to go.

<3

My dad sold my fucking car.. He just sold it! With out asking me, or even telling me for that matter. Fuck that shit. So uhh, I`m not getting my licence, or my permit until he sells that piece of shit 13854341 year old Volvo that he replaced my car with. >_<

Urhg. Anyways.. Yesterday was Cracker Day, which my mom made me attend. It  was boring, &I looked like a drowned rat because it was raining. xD But I saw Pat there. And Mike. hmm..

I think I like someone.. That nobody knows I like because I`m not supposed to like him.-shhdon`ttell.

Today we went to the beach. It was nice.

Yeah.

</3

``Little ants they`re so little I can squash them.``

xD A poem by my little sister. hanna.

``You almost always pick the best times
to drop the worst lines..
You almost made me cry again this time..
Another false alarm.
Red flashing lights..
Well this time I'm not going to watch myself die.
I think I made it a game to play your game 
&let myself cry...
I buried myself alive on the inside,
so I could shut you out
&let you go away for a long time.
``

I`ve been really just like breaking down lately. Everyhting`s been changing so fast, and it`s really crazy. I don`t feel right... Sometime`s it`s really uncomfortable just to breathe, let alone live each day how it is now.. I really need some stability in my life.

 

Shit, emo-ness is fucking taking over. O.o

Shitty day

I hate people.

I miss wrestling. It gave me something to do a few times a week, and now there`s like.. nothing to do.. lmao.

Nick has baseball tonite. I went there the other day, and it reminded me of how much I hate it. >_< It's only fun when the lovely Chelsea's there, but she wasn`t.

I realize I only write in this thing under the following conditions:
*I`m pissed
*Something really good has happened
*I`m incredibly bored.

lol, I just got the weirdest urge to eat cookies.

But we dont have any. >_<

</3

Taste of Chaos was fucking amazing.

Bert... was fucking amazing.

<333*

So I`ve been doing a lot of thinking lately, just about random stuff...

I made a list of people who have made an impact on my life, some good, and some bad. They`re people that I'll remember for years to come.  Mark wanted me to post it, so I guess I will. There`s only a few, and don`t be all upset if you`re a close friend of mine and you`re not on here. And if you wanna know why you`re on it, call me or something. -No specific order-

*Kristi Panko
*Joe Bizzozzaro
*Renee Johnson
*Erica Castine
*Mike Anderson
*Chad Seasney
*Brian Beach
*Katie and Chrissy Weaver
*Shaylyn Gibson
*Britt... I dont know her last name. =P
*Dre Smith

So anyways.. 3 day weekend. woo. =D Saturday, idk what I`m doing. I`m supposed to go to Morgan`s party, but idk if the parental units are gonna let me go.

Tase of Fucking Chaos on Sunday. I can`t wait. It`s gonna be a kick ass time. =]

Monday, I`m planning on going to Erica`s to practice our dance for class. That class is so gay.

Yeah. That`s about it. Don`t bother commenting. Nobody does anyways. =P

<3

Hmm, things are confusing lately..

I broke up with JJ today. he hates me, I know it. Idk why I did.. I just felt like we werent even going out, you know?

urgh, I just dont know..

I have this totally hawt idea for my wall, you guys gotta see it when it's done =D

Progress reports today.
Geometry: A
Science: B, but she fucked it up, it should be an A
History: I didnt get it yet.
Dance: Same ^

I'm doing decent this semester. I'm proud of that A in math though. =]

Leave me some lovin.. I think I need it.
<3

Alie's prediction: Pats win the superbowl, 47-32
Erica's prediction: Eagles win the superbowl, 25-16

Haha. Neither of us know a thing about football.. But our teams are playing against other, so we decided to make a prediction. haha

And Partiots are going to win.

I hope. =D

Dude, I fucking watched a million and seven movies this weekend. haha. I saw Hide and Seek on Friday with Nick and his girlfriend or whatever. It was good. And I saw Jordon there. hahah

hmm. yeah.

<3333333333

People are pointless. Rumors are pointless. Everything is pointless.

Hmm, I've been really caught up with wrestling lately.. It's getting close to the end of the season, and there's a lot of shit that we have to get done. There's a home match on Wednesday nite. Everyone go. =D

I've been working on my history project all weekend. It's getting aggravating. >_<

J.J. said he'd come over today. =D Things with me and him are going good. <3

Erica might come over later too. wh00t. She's the bestest friend. <3

Ugh, idk..... Things are fine one second, and fucked up the next.. I think I'm bipolar.

<3

I stole this from Jordon's journal 'cause I'm a loser like that. =D

girl died in 1933 by a homicidal murderer. He buried her in the ground when she was still alive. The murdered chanted, "Toma sota balcu" as he buried her. Now that you have read the chant, you will meet this little girl. In the middle of the night she will be on your ceiling. She will suffocate you like she was suffocated. If you post this, she will not bother you. Your kindness will be rewarded. 

I got back from the wrestling match a little while ago. Another royal ass-whooping, might I add. I thought we were gonna suck this season, but I was wrong. Hopefully we'll go undefeated again. That would be awesome =]

Homework sucks big hairy man ass. lmao Erica.

Mmm. Taste of Chaos Tour is comming up soon, and I have nobody to go with. And I'm not about to go with Nick. So hit me up if you wanna come.

Later dawgies.
<3*

Man, I've had a long ass weekend.

Rotary was on Friday and Saturday. I got out of school all day Friday which was cool. They had me running a table the whole day though so that kinda sucked. But Oh well, it was fun. haha

Saturday I was in the JV room filling out 354351354684 million bracket sheets. I swear, I'm never writing again. Then I ran a table during finals, and I ended up going to the walk in movie for like 30 minutes.

Yesterday I went to the lovely Erica's house and chilled. We had fun. hehe. Omg, I almost pissed my pants at dinner, I was laughing so hard. Her dad knocked over his beer and he's like "oh damn" so he picks it up and knocks it over again! Then he's all like 'I meant to do it that time..' lmfao he's too funny.

Today I'm just chillen... I wanna see JJ. My mom said he came over twice this weekend, but I wasnt home. =/

That's about it. Payce out.
<333

Wow. A lot of things are going on, and it's all really confusing. Mostly with my love life.

I just dont know what the fuck is going on anymore.

Matt's pissed at me, cause I told him I didnt wanna go out with him. I've liked him for the longest time, but I dont know why I said no. So I lost a good friend.

I dont really know Michael too well, but he's really nice. I dont know if we'll end up going out or what.

-sigh-

Today's been long.

</3
